                <h3>Automation of<br>Auditing Emails</h3>
                <img class="project-img" src="/images/vba_emails.png" alt="VBA Project Image">
                <p>This project involved sending auditing emails to external law firms. Braskem has several law firms representing different types of lawsuits, each with a different email structure and template. The process was executed by different members of the organization, taking 4 to 5 hours to complete. I created a panel with 6 different buttons (each representing a cycle of the auditing process) and successfully sent all emails in 10 seconds. This project resulted in 95% efficiency and 100% accuracy.</p>
