                <img class="project-img" src="/images/powerbiDashboards.png" alt="Power BI Dashboard Image">
                <p>While working at Braskem S.A. in the Legal Efficiency department, I developed Power BI dashboards to track KPIs related to legal operations. These dashboards provided real-time insights into the company's current and past scenarios. By connecting it to a SharePoint database, I enabled the department to efficiently monitor and analyze their status. This project significantly improved decision-making processes and the department's effectiveness.</p>
